[thinking] **Considering API and Mockito**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about the need for a public API that shouldn't have any reflections. When using Mockito, I found that serializing across classloaders can trigger a proxy constructor during the writeObject method and invoke readResolve during readObject. So, it seems like I need to ensure I have existing tests to help validate this. I want to cover all bases and make sure everything works correctly!
